{"tid":20261,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人分唔到紫色同藍色","createTime":"2016-12-03T09:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T05:50:52.000Z","uid":52068,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a54c8d72b5ff67b049c9cc42c417547899782a40","tid":20261,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T09:17:28.000Z","msg":"唔知開係咩台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時比兩隻色我，我就睇到咩分別<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但叫我單睇一隻色，就分唔到係<span style=\"color: blue;\">紫色</span>定<span style=\"color: purple;\">藍色</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實咁係咪叫色弱"},{"pid":"7d0585b4b2f4f828a2e54b02835c36450b964b45","tid":20261,"uid":9034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T09:19:50.000Z","msg":"我分唔到[black]深藍色[/black]同[black]黑色[/black]"},{"pid":"e9778c4876762ac41e4a11c5f34d0580a772ecdf","tid":20261,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T09:26:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我分唔到[black]深藍色[/black]同[black]黑色[/black]</blockquote><br />\n有時D化學反應真係分唔到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ae966d2a3e9033310d721842e4b699bb2c60ee","tid":20261,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T10:22:37.000Z","msg":"有無做過d咩色覺測試"},{"pid":"404c8cb8c1fe4575c5ab07614c6a6c8800f02884","tid":20261,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T10:59:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無做過d咩色覺測試</blockquote><br />\n以前身體檢查同個醫生講過，之後佢攞左排顏色棋出黎叫排深淺色<br />\n<br />\n佢話&ldquo;你對顏色好似唔係咁敏感wo&rdquo;就冇然後啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40db0cfaddcc51abf617add6c5aef5daf70cb47f","tid":20261,"uid":21629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:02:41.000Z","msg":"其實呢兩隻色分別好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打不如做次視力檢查睇下"},{"pid":"c3658e